Please make a statement about what happened.

12
00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:46,660
Later. It's... It's too difficult for me right now.

13
00:01:46,660 --> 00:01:49,620
I'll pack my things and leave.

14
00:01:49,620 --> 00:01:51,360
All right. Go ahead.

15
