01:02:28,680 --> 01:02:32,790
Hey, hey. Now is the chance. Yes.

750
01:02:33,780 --> 01:02:36,740
Hyun Kyung must be disturbed, too.

751
01:02:36,740 --> 01:02:40,700
Let's try to have a more firm resolve.

752
01:02:40,700 --> 01:02:43,970
Hey, we have to find an apartment in two months.

753
01:02:43,970 --> 01:02:46,820
Are you going to move into a study dorm with our children?

754
01:02:46,820 --> 01:02:49,110
It's too small.

755
01:02:50,240 --> 01:02:51,660
Ahjumma, you can't leave.

756
01:02:51,660 --> 01:02:53,390
Wait.

757
01:03:00,070 --> 01:03:03,150
Stay put. If you take off again...

758
01:03:06,850 --> 01:03:09,080
What are you doing?

759
01:03:09,080 --> 01:03:11,830
- Is something wrong? 
 - Be quiet.

760
01:03:18,880 --> 01:03:21,760

761
01:03:26,430 --> 01:03:29,850
Yoon Sae Bom, are you safe?

762
01:03:29,850 --> 01:03:33,370
Do you now know why the lockdown is necessary?

763
01:03:50,920 --> 01:03:53,960
Who, who...

764
01:04:06,160 --> 01:04:08,340
It's all over for other buildings.

765
01:04:08,340 --> 01:04:10,310
I know.

766
01:04:32,290 --> 01:04:34,900

767
01:04:36,180 --> 01:04:39,040
♫  Realize  ♫

768
01:04:39,040 --> 01:04:44,360

769
01:04:47,030 --> 01:04:53,960

770
01:05:00,630 --> 01:05:03,110
 If you're in danger, don't hesitate.

771
01:05:03,110 --> 01:05:04,650
 Don't open the door and stop them.

772
01:05:04,650 --> 01:05:07,460
 Does it make sense that they were all infected in that time?

773
01:05:07,460 --> 01:05:10,480
 What if the situation isn't over after one week?

774
01:05:10,480 --> 01:05:14,710
 We have to have as much food as we can gather.

775
01:05:14,710 --> 01:05:18,120
 We just have to keep the downstairs couple quiet.

776
01:05:18,120 --> 01:05:20,020
 Are you thirsty?

777
01:05:20,020 --> 01:05:23,760
 You can't let them pity the infected. You have to make them fear them and want to run from them.

778
01:05:23,760 --> 01:05:25,150
 Give me water!

779
01:05:25,150 --> 01:05:29,910
 If you're human, why don't you have a sense of responsibility, at least?
